title: Grimm 003 (2013) (Tablet Edition)
description:
This is from the original scanner. I adjusted the resolution and 

compressed the file for easier reading on tablets and ereaders. I 

have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.
  

Grimm 003

By:   	David Greenwalt, Jose Malaga, Lucio Parillo	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Fantasy
Series:   	Grimm
Publisher:   	Dynamite Entertainment	
Pub. Date:  	July 10, 2013


Nick, Hank, and Monroe quest to destroy the Coins of Zakynthos, but 

are caught in the middle of a centuries-long Wesen war. Surrounded 

by players with unclear agendas, the gang forges a reluctant 

alliance, as Kelly makes an escape from her captors!
